  5. CHI-SQUARED CONSISTENCY (Final Iteration)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Chi^2 ~ (H(x)-y)^T R^{-1} (H(x)-y).  E[Chi^2/P] = 1.0 if R,B correct.
  JEDI prints Jo = 1/2 * Chi^2, so Chi^2/P = 2 * (Jo/P).

